    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a dependable choice for a daily driver. While the exterior and interior are clean and presentable, you may find some minor cosmetic wear, such as small stone chips on the hood and light creasing on the driver's seat leather. All major systems are fully functional, and it has a consistent service history, ensuring it is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
