    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive refinement, this vehicle is offered in superlative, showroom condition. Meticulously preserved and maintained to an exacting standard, it features a flawless exterior profile complemented by a pristine, original interior. This acquisition represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to secure a vehicle of uncompromising quality and provenance. Every component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our premier standards of excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
